subject: Fix layout presets to match their SVG icons
body:
- thirds-horizontal/thirds-vertical: Update layouts from 25/50/25 to
  33/34/33 (true equal thirds) to match icons and differentiate from
  feature-center/feature-middle layouts
- mosaic-left/mosaic-right: Update icons from 4 areas to 3 areas to
  match actual layout cell count
